      "versionNonce": 887425937,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772564705185,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Vale a pena ser multi-tenant?",
      "fontSize": 61.62933349609377,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Vale a pena ser multi-tenant?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "t-3TZ4JsZVqgr-tLhI3qa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 420.7589648769922,
      "y": 1720.4010019146417,
      "width": 1364.5435791015625,
      "height": 135,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#2a5da7",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2J",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1756588927,
      "version": 371,
      "versionNonce": 876573041,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772564705185,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "A volumetria pode ser um impeditivo para manter várias empresas sustentadas\nem uma mesma infra.\nTer todos os dados em um mesmo pacote pode abrir brechas de segurança; ",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A volumetria pode ser um impeditivo para manter várias empresas sustentadas\nem uma mesma infra.\nTer todos os dados em um mesmo pacote pode abrir brechas de segurança; ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "6pWeBkwdz5cyp-ME94sUT",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 422.7844900457592,
      "y": 1881.3117057856273,
      "width": 1374.155517578125,
      "height": 90,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "#2a5da7",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2K",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 646810961,
      "version": 618,
      "versionNonce": 185736017,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772564705185,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Como modelo de negócio, pode ser caro MANTER várias estruturas diferentes;\nPrecificação por volume de dados? Focar em clientes pequenos para MVP?",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Como modelo de negócio, pode ser caro MANTER várias estruturas diferentes;\nPrecificação por volume de dados? Focar em clientes pequenos para MVP?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "UvoCY7jgB9Ba-Ki8vqblv",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2329.9421049494813,
      "y": 1617.9011232542457,
      "width": 1226.5834001357325,
      "height": 77.5611623128257,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#2a5da7",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2L",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 332753617,
      "version": 300,
      "versionNonce": 57660735,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772564728218,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Vale a pena ser OpenSource/OnPremisse?",
      "fontSize": 62.048929850260556,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Vale a pena ser OpenSource/OnPremisse?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zQUiQ4yguuVy_xburSJrJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2406.5913520443023,
      "y": 1720.6336873106072,
      "width": 1491.44384765625,
      "height": 90,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#2a5da7",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2M",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1818355889,
      "version": 585,
      "versionNonce": 1564023391,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772564789152,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "OpenSource pode aumentar a confiabilidade no produto, uma vez que o próprio código\npode ser auditado por orgãos externos - inclusive pelos peritos.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "OpenSource pode aumentar a confiabilidade no produto, uma vez que o próprio código\npode ser auditado por orgãos externos - inclusive pelos peritos.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "jlQlHzIkgPS08_x0JUtqm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4956.549155921876,
      "y": 146.44576628767845,
      "width": 575.0076293945308,
      "height": 997.5852582952967,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "#2a5da7",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2O",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1011844895,
      "version": 261,
      "versionNonce": 1745357834,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776709382712,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "{\n    \"specversion\" : \"1.0.1\",\n    \"type\" : \"AuditEvent\",\n    \"source\" : \"https://www.example.com/\",\n    \"id\" : \"app-domain-key\",\n    \"time\" : \"2020-04-05T17:31:00Z\",\n    \"contenttype\" : \"application/json\",\n    \"data\" : {\n        \"appInfo\" : {\n            \"appname\" : \"example-app\",\n            \"domain\" : \"sales\",\n            \"version\" : \"1.0.0\"\n        },\n        \"user\" : {\n            \"id\" : \"12345\",\n            \"name\" : \"John Doe\",\n            \"role\": \"admin\"\n        },\n        \"operation\" : {\n            \"type\" : \"insert\",\n            \"entity\" : \"users\",\n            \"generatedAt\" : \"2020-04-05T17:30:00Z\",\n            \"transmittedAt\" : \"2020-04-05T17:31:00Z\"\n        },\n        \"index\": {\n            \"indexField1\": \"value1\",\n            \"indexField2\": \"value2\"\n        },\n        \"data\" : {\n            \"id\" : \"12345\",\n            \"name\" : \"John Doe\",\n            \"email\" : \"mail@to.com\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n",
      "fontSize": 22.16856129545104,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "{\n    \"specversion\" : \"1.0.1\",\n    \"type\" : \"AuditEvent\",\n    \"source\" : \"https://www.example.com/\",\n    \"id\" : \"app-domain-key\",\n    \"time\" : \"2020-04-05T17:31:00Z\",\n    \"contenttype\" : \"application/json\",\n    \"data\" : {\n        \"appInfo\" : {\n            \"appname\" : \"example-app\",\n            \"domain\" : \"sales\",\n            \"version\" : \"1.0.0\"\n        },\n        \"user\" : {\n            \"id\" : \"12345\",\n            \"name\" : \"John Doe\",\n            \"role\": \"admin\"\n        },\n        \"operation\" : {\n            \"type\" : \"insert\",\n            \"entity\" : \"users\",\n            \"generatedAt\" : \"2020-04-05T17:30:00Z\",\n            \"transmittedAt\" : \"2020-04-05T17:31:00Z\"\n        },\n        \"index\": {\n            \"indexField1\": \"value1\",\n            \"indexField2\": \"value2\"\n        },\n        \"data\" : {\n            \"id\" : \"12345\",\n            \"name\" : \"John Doe\",\n            \"email\" : \"mail@to.com\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n",
      "autoResize": true,
